<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>To <%= @invitation.name %>,</p>

    <p>Thank you for your response.</p>

    <p>Your invitation is attached to this email.</p>

    <% if @invitees.blank? %>
        <p>We're sorry you cannot make it to our wedding, but thank you for being part of our life.</p>
    <% else %>
        <p>We look forward to seeing the following guests at the wedding.</p>

        <ul>
            <% @invitees.each do |invitee| %>
                <li><%= invitee.name %></li>
            <% end %>
        </ul>

        <p>Thank you for being a part of our wedding.</p>
    <% end %>

    <p>If any of these details are incorrect please contact us immediately.</p>

    <p>Thank you,</p>
    <p>Amy &amp; Kevin</p>
  </body>
</html>
